{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place buckwheat grains in mixing bowl and grind <b>1 min\/speed 10<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then grind again <b>30 sec\/speed 10<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add almonds and 120 g pumpkin seeds then grind <b>40 sec\/speed 10<b>.","Add sunflower seeds, linseeds, chia seeds, psyllium husks, fresh thyme leaves, salt, water and remaining 60 g pumpkin seeds then mix <b>15 sec\/\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Mix again <b>15 sec\/\/speed 3<b>. Grease a 450 g loaf tin with olive oil and transfer mixture to tin. Even out top of dough with back of oiled spatula then cover and leave to rest for 1 hour.","Preheat oven to 180°C. Bake loaf 50 minutes (180°C) or until top is brown and skewer inserted in centre comes out clean. Cool for 10 minutes in tin before transferring to a wire rack. Cool completely before cutting in slices."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["100 g buckwheat grains, raw","120 g blanched almonds","180 g pumpkin seeds","60 g sunflower seeds","60 g linseeds","30 g chia seeds","30 g psyllium husks","1 heaped tsp fresh thyme leaves","1 tsp fine sea salt","300 g water","olive oil, for greasing"]}],"id":"r75690","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-f0Un_NQrKls\/XZavBK47qEI\/AAAAAAAAhqI\/DHDozTQykhAK0OQCWdpUAoLBeb0KwzJ3wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_SiKqRhmttmuCo9Av.png","title":"Buckwheat, Almond and Seed Bread","publishedAt":"2015-05-13T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7.6 g","fat":"13.9 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"9.7 g","calories":"814 kJ \/ 195 kcal"},"usefulItems":"450 g loaf tin (1 lb), skewer, cooling rack, oven","basicInfo":["easy","10m","2h","16 slices"]}